  <p align="left"><font face="Courier New, Courier, mono" size="2">] Now that 
    I had my computer system, I was ready for business. We got our own phone line 
    and started calling bulletin boards like crazy.. Running our phone bill up 
    to $200 a month with no slowing down... Our phone bills were going up, up 
    and up... We had to do something about this, so we started experimenting with 
    calling card companies.. Our local long distance company was called LDS (Long 
    Distance Service) and we got them good.. I cooincidentally saw a post on a 
    bulletin board which gave an actually calling card # that worked for the SKYLINE 
    long distance company. This same number worked on LDS, but what we soon found 
    out was that LDS had only 1000 calling card numbers issued and they were all 
    issued between 56xxxx and 57xxxx.. So we ran a hacking program over a 2 day 
    period and managed to take all their calling cards numbers with one big SWOOOOOP. 
    Now we were set, we could make all the phone calls - anytime - anywhere in 
    the world without having to worry about any more phone bills or parents breathing 
    down our necks for making expensive phone calls. The most exciting thing about 
    this was that we lived in an area where tracing was impossible, our phone 
    system was so primitive that even the operator didnt know where I was calling 
    from! This gave us confidence and allowed us to do what we wanted in relation 
    to long distance phone calls.</font></p>
  <p align="left"><font face="Courier New, Courier, mono" size="2">] It didnt 
    stop here! We talked our parents into buying us a 10 meg external hard drive 
    (by a company called RANA ELITE). At the time it was the biggest hard drive 
    made and it cost my parents $1200... Believe me.. We were now considered ELITE! 
    We also managed to get the hacker's choice modem called the NOVATION APPLE 
    CAT ][ modem. This modem was able to do 300 bps + 1200 bps in half duplex.. 
    We were also able to clone operator tones and do speed dialing. This cut our 
    hacking time in half (hahahahaha). We had now had everything we needed for 
    our own bulletin board system (BBS).</font></p>
  <p><img src="EVILEXIDY/apple2_jon.jpg" width="288" height="216"></p>
  <p><font color="#FFFFFF">Actual picture of our apple //e. (pictured above: scott 
    (left), me (right))</font></p>
  <p><font color="#FF0000">[*] The Silent World Cat-Fur 10 Megs......318-357-0858 
    [*]</font></p>
  <p align="left"><font face="Courier New, Courier, mono" size="2">] After thinking 
    of some cool names we decided to go with (k)uality (k)onnections aka &quot;The 
    Silent World&quot; BBS - which ran as a BBS, CAT-FUR and AE. At the time (k) 
    meant COOL or better yet - Kool. So the more K's that were used, the kooler 
    your bbs. I also joined the pirate group known as COAST TO COAST. So all the 
    software that was cracked by them had our phone number listed on it. I was 
    only 12 years old and my brother was 11, but we were doing stuff that most 
    people couldnt even imagine for its time. </font></p>
  <p align="left"><font face="Courier New, Courier, mono" size="2">] By this time 
    we already had thousands of games and access to everything we ever wanted. 
    We even picked up how to CC (credi card). This is where people jump in dumbsters 
    and steal the credit card carbon copies and use them to order merchandise 
    (including computer parts, games, anything!!). You can imagine what happened 
    here, I just leave it at that :)</font></p>
  <p align="left"><font face="Courier New, Courier, mono" size="2">] ...This period 
    of chaos/adventure in my life ended in 1985/1986 when several of my friends 
    were arrested for phreaking. I was tipped-off almost a month before the FBI 
    came to my house. The tip was given by a friend of mine (king Lear).. He called 
    me from a phone booth and explained to what had happened to him and his BBS, 
    he also stated that FBI was asking questions about us (my brother and I) and 
    our BBS. Later that week I managed to hide all my hardcore hacking/phreaking 
    equipment plus all our illegal software. We set up a bare bones 'skeleton 
    computer' which was taken by the FBI when they came to our house.</font></p>
  <p align="left"><font face="Courier New, Courier, mono" size="2">] The FBI. 
    This was a scary time for our parents, but I can honestly say it wasnt for 
    my brother and I. When the FBI came over and when they introduced themselves 
    my parents were scared stiff. Both my brother and I were cool and calm, because 
    we knew they were coming so we had already prepared for it. They asked us 
    questions, more questions, and even more questions.. They were determined 
    to break us.. We never did! We denied everything.. They even asked to see 
    our computer which we were more than happy to show them. They took our computer 
    away from us which ended our rampage. <br>
    In the end we were never defeated but our parents cracked down on us and would 
    not allow us to dial into any BBS's anymore. Plus by this time we were in 
    our mid teens and had bigger and better things to do.</font></p>
